    all other level 4 or lower Digimon to the hand. For each card placed in this
    Digimon's digivolution cards, add 1 to the level this effect may return.\n[Your
    Turn] [Once Per Turn] When an effect places a digivolution card under this Digimon,
    you may play 1 level 5 or lower Digimon card with [Aqua]/[Sea Animal]\_in one
    of its traits from this Digimon's digivolution cards without paying the cost.\n[Rule]
